(1484, 'widget_black-studio-tinymce', 'a:3:{i:2;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:0:"";s:4:"text";s:1080:"<h3>Rent Direct from the Owner &amp; Save Mon</h3>\r\n<p>By contacting the owner or his representative you are cutting out the many middlemen who are sometimes involved, either resulting in the price escalating or the owner receiving less.</p>\r\n<p>You can email the owner and ask whatever relevant questions you feel, and if you wish to rent the in the low season or at the last minute you can always make him an offer, after all one per is better than no per cent.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Remember when you book using PayPal you are protected.</strong></p>\r\n<h3>Easy communication between Renter &amp; Owner</h3>\r\n<p>Whenever you wish to contact the owner just fill in the request form and you can email him. An SMS contact message will be sent immediately informing that an email from you has arrived.</p>\r\n<p>Once you have established contact most owners will willingly give you a contact number .</p>\r\n<h3>No Hidden Fees</h3>\r\n<p>Unlike some property website there are no hidden fees, no commission at all is payable. The amount quoted when making your Subscription is what you pay.</p>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}i:3;a:3:{s:5:"title";s:6:"Prices";s:4:"text";s:1187:"<p><strong>Monthly Subscription:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>First property: £ 19.95 / 25 €</li>\r\n<li>Second property: £ 14.95 / 19 €</li>\r\n<li>Third property: £ 9.95 / 12 €</li>\r\n<li>Forth and thereafter: £ 4.95 / 6 €</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Half Yearly Subscription:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>First property: £ 109.95 / 140 €</li>\r\n<li>Second property: £ 79.95 / 102 €</li>\r\n<li>Third property: £ 59.95 / 76 €</li>\r\n<li>Fourth property: £ 49.95 / 63 €</li>\r\n<li>Fifth and thereafter: £ 24.95 / 32 €</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Annual Subscription:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>First property: £ 199.95 / 255 €</li>\r\n<li>Second property: £ 149.95 / 190 €</li>\r\n<li>Third property: £ 99.95 / 127 €</li>\r\n<li>Fourth property: £ 49.95 / 63 €</li>\r\n<li>Fifth and thereafter:: £ 44.95 / 57 €</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<h3>"Featured Property" Area</h3>\r\n<p>Add your properties to be showcased in the premium “Featured Property” area. This enhancement to you subscription will increase your property visibility and attract more potential customers.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Monthly: £ 4.95 each</li>\r\n<li>Half Yearly: £ 3.95 each</li>\r\n<li>Annual: £ 3.95 each</li>\r\n</ul>";s:4:"type";s:6:"visual";}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes'),
