(533, 1, '2012-09-23 15:39:35', '2012-09-23 15:39:35', '<p><a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/siampark-1.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-536" title="siampark-1" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/siampark-1-231x240.jpg" alt="" width="231" height="240" /></a>Siam Park provides a perfect day out for families, groups of friends and conference and incentive teams. Inspired by the old King of Thailand, Siam, the water park is the largest in Europe with more than a 52 million euro investment and 185,000 square metres of thrilling attractions along with 25 ‘Thai’ style buildings. As well as all the exhilarating attractions there are numerous restaurants, bars, cocktail bars, chill out areas and even a Thai floating market!</p>', 'Siam Park', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'siam-park', '', '', '2012-09-23 15:42:31', '2012-09-23 15:42:31', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=533', 0, 'location', '', 0),
