(542, 1, '2012-09-23 17:37:35', '2012-09-23 17:37:35', '<p><a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/jungle-park-1.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-544" title="jungle-park-1" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/jungle-park-1-300x215.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="215" /></a>Jungle Park (Las Aguilas Parque) is a spectacular zoological and botanical park in the mountains of Aguilas del Teide and yet less than 10 minutes away from Los Cristianos. Jungle Park provides approximately 75,000m2 of natural habitat in which over 500 animals live including, chimps, gibbons and big cats. Don’t miss the bird shows where you can experience birds of prey and colourful exotic birds in free flight displaying their skills.</p>', 'Jungle Park', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jungle-park', '', '', '2012-09-23 17:37:35', '2012-09-23 17:37:35', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=542', 0, 'location', '', 0),
