(316, 1, '2012-07-29 16:08:21', '2012-07-29 16:08:21', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-amarilla-pic.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-374" title="golf-amarilla-pic" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-amarilla-pic-300x208.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="208" /></a>On the southern coast of Tenerife, just bordering the sea, we find the Amarilla Golf and Country Club. First opened in 1989, the character of the 18 hole course is marked by the incredible views of the Atlantic Ocean which, without a doubt, inspired the designer of the course, golf architect Donald Steel.\r\n\r\nThe Golf course, surrounded by barrancos and a residential development, provides a defying challenge for the professional golfer while, at the same time, offers an attractive and enjoyable game for those of a more modest ability.\r\n\r\nThe course, a par 71 is 5,918 metres in length.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Amarilla Golf & Country Club', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'amarilla-golf-country-club', '', '', '2012-09-20 11:36:05', '2012-09-20 11:36:05', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=316', 0, 'location', '', 0),
(317, 1, '2012-07-29 16:12:20', '2012-07-29 16:12:20', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-adeje-pic.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-375" title="golf-adeje-pic" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-adeje-pic-300x221.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="221" /></a> This excellent 27 hole course opened in 1998 has rapidly become one the most popular courses in Tenerife.\r\n\r\nDesigned by the internationally renowned architect Pepe Gancedo the layout adapts itself to the natural terrain and a feature of the course is the restored stone walls and terracing of the former banana plantations that previously occupied the site The stunning views from the course take in the island of La Gomera, the mountain ranges behind Adeje, the resort of Playa de la Americas, and the sea.\r\n\r\nThe championship course of 6,203 metres consists of 18 holes comprising 6 par 5’s, 6 par 4’s and 6 par 3’s.  The shorter 9 hole Los Lagos course comprises 4 par 3’s, 4 par 4’s and 1 par 5.', 'Golf Costa Adeje', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'golf-costa-adeje', '', '', '2012-09-20 00:20:23', '2012-09-20 00:20:23', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=317', 0, 'location', '', 0),
