(320, 1, '2012-08-05 22:16:05', '2012-08-05 22:16:05', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-buenavista-pic.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-376" title="golf-buenavista-pic" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-buenavista-pic-300x196.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="196" /></a>Buenavista Golf is located in the north-western corner of the island of Tenerife, in the region of Daute Isla Baja.  The golf course was designed by Severiano Ballesteros and opened in 2004.\r\n\r\nThe 18 hole, par 72 course, has a length of 6,019 metres and has 6 holes each of par 3, par 4 and par 5.\r\n\r\nThe outstanding holes are closer to the coast and the player seems to hit the ball right into the ocean or into the lake of holes 9 and 18 that are connected by a waterfall', 'Buena Vista Golf', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'buena-vista-golf', '', '', '2012-09-20 00:21:22', '2012-09-20 00:21:22', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=320', 0, 'location', '', 0),
