(234, 1, '2012-08-19 22:20:02', '2012-08-19 22:20:02', 'Flights to Tenerife are presently available from 21 mainland UK airports and 4 airports in Ireland (inc. Belfast Int. in Northern Ireland).\n<h3>Airports serving Tenerife (Reina Sofia Airport) with direct flights.</h3>\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="10">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Airport (Code)</strong></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<ul>\n	<li>Aberdeen (ABZ)</li>\n	<li>Belfast International (BFS)</li>\n	<li>Birmingham (BHX)</li>\n	<li>Blackpool (BLK)</li>\n	<li>Bournemouth (BOH)</li>\n	<li>Bristol (BRS)</li>\n	<li>Cardiff (CWL)</li>\n	<li>Cork (ORK)</li>\n	<li>Doncaster Sheffield (DSA)</li>\n	<li>Dublin (DUB)</li>\n	<li>Durham Tees Valley (MME)</li>\n	<li>East Midlands (EMA)</li>\n	<li>Edinburgh (EDI)</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul>\n	<li>Exeter (EXT)</li>\n	<li>Glasgow International (GLA)</li>\n	<li>Glasgow Prestwick (PIK)</li>\n	<li>Leeds Bradford (LBA)</li>\n	<li>Liverpool (LPL)</li>\n	<li>London Gatwick (LGW)</li>\n	<li>London Luton (LTN)</li>\n	<li>London Stansted (STN)</li>\n	<li>Manchester (MAN)</li>\n	<li>Newcastle (NCL)</li>\n	<li>Norwich  (NWI)</li>\n	<li>Shannon (SNN)</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>Eight airlines currently offer flights to Tenerife from the UK &amp; Ireland:</h3>\n<table width="520" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align="center" valign="middle" width="130" height="100"><a href="http://www.aerlingus.com/home/index.jsp" target="_blank"><img class="no-photo-frame" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/airline-aireuropa.jpg" alt="" width="130" height="100" /></a></td>\n<td align="center" valign="middle" width="130" height="100"><a href="http://www.easyjet.com/asp/en/book/index.asp?lang=en" target="_blank"><img class="no-photo-frame" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/airline-aerlingus.jpg" alt="" width="130" height="100" /></a></td>\n<td align="center" valign="middle" width="130" height="100"><a href="http://www.jet2.com/" target="_blank"><img class="no-photo-frame" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/airline-easyjet.jpg" alt="" width="130" height="100" /></a></td>\n<td align="center" valign="middle" width="130" height="100"><a href="http://www.monarch.co.uk/" target="_blank"><img class="no-photo-frame" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/airline-jet2.jpg" alt="" width="130" height="100" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align="center" valign="middle" width="130" height="100"><a href="http://www.monarch.co.uk/" target="_blank"><img class="no-photo-frame" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/airline-monarch.jpg" alt="" width="130" height="100" /></a></td>\n<td align="center" valign="middle" width="130" height="100"><a href="http://www.ryanair.com/en" target="_blank"><img class="no-photo-frame" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/airline-ryanair.jpg" alt="" width="130" height="100" /></a></td>\n<td align="center" valign="middle" width="130" height="100"><a href="http://www.skyscanner.net/" target="_blank"><img class="no-photo-frame" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/airline-skyscanner.jpg" alt="" width="130" height="100" /></a></td>\n<td align="center" valign="middle" width="130" height="100"><a href="http://book.flythomascook.com/" target="_blank"><img class="no-photo-frame" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/airline-thomascook.jpg" alt="" width="130" height="100" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align="center" valign="middle" width="130" height="100"><a href="http://flights.thomson.co.uk/en/index.html" target="_blank"><img class="no-photo-frame" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/airline-thomson.jpg" alt="" width="130" height="100" /></a></td>\n<td align="center" valign