(342, 1, '2012-03-07 03:28:29', '2012-03-07 03:28:29', 'Flights to Tenerife are presently available from 21 mainland UK airports and 4 airports in Ireland (inc. Belfast Int. in Northern Ireland).\r\n<h3>Airports serving Tenerife (Reina Sofia Airport) with direct flights.</h3>\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="10">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Airport (Code)</strong></td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Aberdeen (ABZ)</li>\r\n	<li>Belfast International (BFS)</li>\r\n	<li>Birmingham (BHX)</li>\r\n	<li>Blackpool (BLK)</li>\r\n	<li>Bournemouth (BOH)</li>\r\n	<li>Bristol (BRS)</li>\r\n	<li>Cardiff (CWL)</li>\r\n	<li>Cork (ORK)</li>\r\n	<li>Doncaster Sheffield (DSA)</li>\r\n	<li>Dublin (DUB)</li>\r\n	<li>Durham Tees Valley (MME)</li>\r\n	<li>East Midlands (EMA)</li>\r\n	<li>Edinburgh (EDI)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Exeter (EXT)</li>\r\n	<li>Glasgow International (GLA)</li>\r\n	<li>Glasgow Prestwick (PIK)</li>\r\n	<li>Leeds Bradford (LBA)</li>\r\n	<li>Liverpool (LPL)</li>\r\n	<li>London Gatwick (LGW)</li>\r\n	<li>London Luton (LTN)</li>\r\n	<li>London Stansted (STN)</li>\r\n	<li>Manchester (MAN)</li>\r\n	<li>Newcastle (NCL)</li>\r\n	<li>Norwich  (NWI)</li>\r\n	<li>Shannon (SNN)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>Eight airlines currently offer flights to Tenerife from the UK &amp; Ireland:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.aerlingus.com/home/index.jsp" target="_blank"><strong>Air Europa</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.easyjet.com/asp/en/book/index.asp?lang=en" target="_blank"><strong>Aer Lingus</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.jet2.com/" target="_blank"><strong>easyJet</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.monarch.co.uk/" target="_blank"><strong>Jet2</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.ryanair.com/en" target="_blank"><strong>Ryanair</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://book.flythomascook.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Thomas Cook</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://flights.thomson.co.uk/en/index.html" target="_blank"><strong>Thompson</strong></a></li>\r\n	<li><a href="http://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=monarch%20airlines&amp;source=web&amp;cd=1&amp;sqi=2&amp;ved=0CE8QFjAA&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.monarch.co.uk%2F&amp;ei=xtVWT7jgE-PY0QGUqY2PCg&amp;usg=AFQjCNGCEpX7o_VorehIddx8NcZmQKuZvQ&amp;cad=rja" target="_blank"><strong>Monarch</strong></a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFrom this information you will gather there is a wide choice of options.\r\nSo where’s the best place to start?   A good general flight search engine!\r\n\r\n<strong>Tenerife-Apartments recommends <a href="http://www.skyscanner.net/" target="_blank">Skyscanner.</a></strong>\r\n\r\nWhen using this site it’s a good idea to search for flights from your chosen airport for the complete month rather than particular dates.  You may find by adjusting your departure and return dates you can save money on the flight element of your holiday.\r\n\r\nWhy not consider travelling on days other than the traditional Tenerife flight days.  Sometimes a 6 day or 13 day holiday can save considerably on flight costs.\r\n\r\nWhy not consider using different airlines for the outbound and inbound flights.  This could result in more socially acceptable arrival times both in Tenerife and in the UK and should not increase overall flight   costs.\r\n\r\nDon’t ignore the cheap package-holiday offers that line up with your proposed holiday dates.  These offers may afford a better deal than a flight only option and you simply dump the package-holiday accommodation on arrival in Tenerife.', 'Flights', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '148-revision-5', '', '', '2012-03-07 03:28:29', '2012-03-07 03:28:29', '', 148, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/148-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
