(381, 1, '2012-09-20 11:22:30', '2012-09-20 11:22:30', 'Tenerife is blessed with seven golf courses plus a short nine hole course at Los Palos. The high season for golf in Tenerife runs from October thru to April.  Early booking of tee times is advised during this period with green fees ranging from 80€ up to 200€.\r\n\r\nDuring the off season, May thru to September, it is possible to book a tee time at a moments notice and green fees drop to as little as 40€. In the south of the Island there is also a short nine hole course, Los Palo, where green fees are less than 30€ for 18 holes.\r\n\r\n[locations category="13" addresses=”true” type="map" sort_by="title"]', 'Golf Courses', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '297-revision-23', '', '', '2012-09-20 11:22:30', '2012-09-20 11:22:30', '', 297, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/297-revision-23/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(382, 1, '2012-09-20 11:27:18', '2012-09-20 11:27:18', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-de-las-americas-pic.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-383" title="golf-de-las-americas-pic" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-de-las-americas-pic-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /></a>Golf las Américas is situated in the Heart of Playa de Las AméricasThe course is noted for its excellent condition throughout the year.  Having hosted International tournaments both amateur and professional, Golf Las Américas is a championship 18 hole par 72 course with an overall length of 6.051 meters (6.617 yards).\r\n\r\nThe course opened in 1998 and was designed by John Jacobs &amp; Associates.  The course covers over 90 hectares of land is situated in the heart of Playa de Las Americas and one of it’s most notable features is its streams, ravines and lakes which cross the course. Water comes in to play on the 1st, 2nd, 3rd, 5th 12th, 13th, 17th and 18th holes.\r\n\r\nThe clubhouse overlooks the 18th fairway and green and both the 1st and 10th tees are also located close to the clubhouse.', 'Golf Las Américas', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'golf-las-americas', '', '', '2012-09-20 11:27:18', '2012-09-20 11:27:18', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=382', 0, 'location', '', 0),
