(385, 1, '2012-09-20 11:31:25', '2012-09-20 11:31:25', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-real-pic.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-386" title="golf-real-pic" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-real-pic-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></a>The Real Club de Golf de Tenerife was founded on the 18th December 1932, which makes it the second oldest in Spain. The course is located in the greenest and coolest part of the island of Tenerife, at 600 to 753 meters above sea level and within the municipality of Tacoronte. It has 18 holes, a total circuit length of 5740 metres and a par of 71.\r\n\r\nThe beauty of its landscape lies, among other details, on the abundance of mature trees, which blend in perfectly with the other course elements.', 'Real Club de Golf', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'real-club-de-golf', '', '', '2012-09-20 11:34:59', '2012-09-20 11:34:59', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=385', 0, 'location', '', 0),
