(388, 1, '2012-09-20 11:38:30', '2012-09-20 11:38:30', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-los-palos-pic.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-389" title="golf-los-palos-pic" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-los-palos-pic-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></a>Don’t be fooled into writing it off because it is a short course, ''Los Palos'' is certainly not a pitch and putt and there are plenty of challenges to be encountered over its 914 metres: five holes are affected by water and others require very accurate hitting.\r\n\r\nOpened in December 1994 Golf Tenerife ''Los Palos'' was designed by José Maria Olazábal´s company, Integral Golf Design, and is located on the TF66 road between Guaza and Las Galletas.  The course has a slight inclination is surrounded by banana trees and is the perfect place to spend a couple of hours on a round of golf, or become familiar with the game.  Los Palos is the perfect golf facility for those wishing to golf for an hour or so. Los Palos also boasts a comprehensive practice area for those wishing to tune up their game.', 'Los Palos Golf', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'los-palos-golf', '', '', '2012-09-20 11:38:30', '2012-09-20 11:38:30', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=388', 0, 'location', '', 0),
