(409, 1, '2012-09-22 20:45:58', '2012-09-22 20:45:58', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/san-eugenio.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-411" title="san-eugenio" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/san-eugenio-300x208.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="208" /></a>San Eugenio Bajo is a natural extension of Playa de las Americas and falls in the municipality of Adeje.  It extends from Pueblo Canario in the south to Hotel La Niña in the north and runs back from the coast as far as the TF1 motorway.  San Eugenio is home to some 26 hotels and apartment complexes, it hosts the La Pinta beach and is home to the Puerto Colon Marina.\r\n\r\nThe UPS Costa Adeje Hospital is situated in San Eugenio just off the TF1 motorway.  San Eugenio Bajo is 19kms from Tenerife’s South Airport, a journey that takes about 20 minutes.', 'San Eugenio Bajo', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'san-eugenio-bajo', '', '', '2012-09-22 20:53:55', '2012-09-22 20:53:55', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=409', 0, 'location', '', 0),
