(414, 1, '2012-09-22 21:07:20', '2012-09-22 21:07:20', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/san-eugenio-alto.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-415" title="san-eugenio-alto" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/san-eugenio-alto-300x224.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="224" /></a>San Eugenio Alto lies on the eastern side of the TF1 Motorway and it’s stunning sea views make up for the fact that is some 5 minutes walk to the coast.\r\n\r\nSan Eugenio extends from the Exit Palace in the south up to Aqualand in the north and is home to some 19 apartment complexes in addition to many private villas.  San Eugenio Alto is 19kms from Tenerife’s South Airport, a journey that takes just 19 minutes.<strong><em></em></strong>', 'San Eugenio Alto', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'san-eugenio-alto', '', '', '2012-09-22 21:07:34', '2012-09-22 21:07:34', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=414', 0, 'location', '', 0),
