(422, 1, '2012-09-22 21:28:17', '2012-09-22 21:28:17', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/fanabe.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-423" title="fanabe" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/fanabe-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></a>The resort area of Fañabe lies just off the 1km. long beach of the same name.  It is located just north of Torviscas Bajo in the municipality of Adeje and is home to 18 hotel and apartment complexes. Its close proximity to Playa Fañabe makes it a firm favourite with families and the beach promenade is well supplied with bars, restaurants, shops, and attractions to keep the whole family entertained.  The south airport is just 21 kms distant and the journey takes just a little over 20 minutes.', 'Fañabe', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fanabe', '', '', '2012-09-22 21:29:17', '2012-09-22 21:29:17', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=422', 0, 'location', '', 0),
