(424, 1, '2012-09-22 21:30:06', '2012-09-22 21:30:06', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/costa-adeje.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-425" title="costa-adeje" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/costa-adeje-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></a>Although the title Costa Adeje is used by the municipality to designate all its coastal resorts including San Eugenio, Torviscas, and Fañabe, the Costa Adeje resort area really starts at the northern end of Fañabe and extends towards La Caleta.\r\n\r\nIt is the newest of the resort areas of South Tenerife and houses some of the finest hotels and apartment complexes on the Island.  In all there are in excess of 26 hotels villa, and apartment complexes including the renowned Gran Hotel Bahia del Duque.  The area is served by the Playa del Duque beach and is home to some up-market shopping areas featuring many of the worlds best known labels.  Costa Adeje is some 25kms from the Tenerife South Airport, a journey that takes less than 30 minutes.', 'Costa Adeje', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'costa-adeje', '', '', '2012-09-22 21:30:06', '2012-09-22 21:30:06', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=424', 0, 'location', '', 0),
