(426, 1, '2012-09-22 21:32:06', '2012-09-22 21:32:06', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/la-caleta.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-427" title="la-caleta" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/la-caleta-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></a>La Caleta, is a small coastal village in the municipality of Adeje just north of Costa Adeje.  La Caleta is home to a small number of apartment complexes but it is more famous for its fish restaurants that sit right on the seafront.  In addition Costa Adeje Golf  is just over a kilometre to the north.  The south airport is 25 kms away, a journey that takes about 25 minutes.', 'La Caleta', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'la-caleta', '', '', '2012-09-22 21:32:06', '2012-09-22 21:32:06', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=426', 0, 'location', '', 0),
