(429, 1, '2012-09-22 21:34:59', '2012-09-22 21:34:59', 'Located on the west coast of Tenerife, Playa Paraiso is a purpose built resort area within the municipality of Adeje and is still being developed so visitors may witness some construction work.  The resort was originally based around four tall apartment blocks but now also includes a number of all-inclusive complexes.  The resort offers a few bars and restaurants with the main entertainment and night-life centred around hotel entertainment.\r\n\r\nFor a greater variety and livelier night-life Playa de las Americas is a short distance away.  Playa Paraiso means Paradise Beach which is a bit of a misnomer as there is only a very small man made beach with golden sand, which is fairly quiet but there is a salt water swimming complex called Lago Paraiso that is ideal for families.   The resort area at 30 kms from Tenerife South Airport is a 30 minute ride away.', 'Playa Paraiso', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'playa-paraiso', '', '', '2012-09-22 21:34:59', '2012-09-22 21:34:59', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=429', 0, 'location', '', 0),
(430, 1, '2012-09-22 21:36:47', '2012-09-22 21:36:47', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/callao-salvaje.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-431" title="callao-salvaje" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/callao-salvaje-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></a>The village of Callao Salvaje situated in the municipality of Adeje is quiet, peaceful and relaxing.  Its location makes it a popular area to stay for those who want to be near the ''action'' but not stuck in the middle of it as it is situated between the bustling resort of Playa de Las Americas and the tranquil resort of Los Gigantes.\r\n\r\nOriginally, a small fishing village, over the past few years Callao Salvaje has undergone a rapid transformation. A self-contained village with a mix of residential homes and holiday resort and all the amenities required for both. There are supermarkets, a pharmacy, bars and restaurants, shops, car hire, bank etc and only a 30-minute drive from the airport. There is a beach, which is currently being upgraded and will be completed in the near future.  The South Airport is 30 kms distant, which is little more than 30 minutes away.', 'Callao Salvaje', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'callao-salvaje', '', '', '2012-09-22 21:36:47', '2012-09-22 21:36:47', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=430', 0, 'location', '', 0),
