(434, 1, '2012-09-22 21:39:50', '2012-09-22 21:39:50', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/marazul.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-435" title="marazul" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/marazul-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></a>Marazul is a stand alone French built holiday complex within the municipality of Adeje. It comprises a main hotel building consisting of very large apartments and further villa style apartments built in the grounds on the slope down to the sea. It boasts a freshwater pool at the hotel and a saltwater pool and club right on the shoreline.  Marazul is 32 kms from the South Airport, a journey that will take a little over 30 minutes.', 'Marazul', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'marazul', '', '', '2012-09-22 21:39:50', '2012-09-22 21:39:50', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=434', 0, 'location', '', 0),
