(438, 1, '2012-09-22 21:42:32', '2012-09-22 21:42:32', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/playa-san-juan.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-437" title="playa-san-juan" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/playa-san-juan-300x236.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="236" /></a>Playa San Juan is a typical Canarian village that has improved its tourist infrastructure without losing any of its charm.  It is located in the municipality of Guia de Isora and is some 37 kms or 40 minutes drive from the South Airport.  It is one of the few remaining working fishing villages in Tenerife and also offers whale and dolphin safaris from the small port.  The new Abama Golf resort is five minutes away and the town hosts a local market twice a week.\n\nThere are 2 beaches to found here, a small cove with shallow waters which is popular with families with small children and the other is a long sandy beach, which has recently been developed. The crystal clear waters make it a favoured diving spot. There is a promenade that runs the full length of the village, which is dotted with restaurants offering international and local cuisines, many with fresh fish specialities. A few small shops and bars can also be found here.<strong></strong>', 'Playa de San Juan', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '436-autosave', '', '', '2012-09-22 21:42:32', '2012-09-22 21:42:32', '', 436, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/436-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(439, 1, '2012-09-22 21:47:26', '2012-09-22 21:47:26', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/alcala.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-440" title="alcala" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/alcala-300x199.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="199" /></a>Alcalá is a small coastal town in the municipality of Guia de Isora.  Apart from tourism its main economies are fishing on a small scale and agriculture the main crops being tomatoes and bananas.  It has some apartment complexes but its major tourist resort is that of the Melia flagship hotel, the Gran Melia Palacio de Isora.\r\n\r\nAlcalá sits on the west coast between Playa San Juan and Los Gigantes and is 39kms, about 40 minutes from the South Airport.', 'Alcalá', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'alcala', '', '', '2012-09-22 21:47:26', '2012-09-22 21:47:26', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=439', 0, 'location', '', 0),
