(447, 1, '2012-09-22 21:56:51', '2012-09-22 21:56:51', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/palm-mar.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-448" title="palm-mar" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/palm-mar-300x208.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="208" /></a>Palm Mar is a quiet residential area in the municipality of Arona just a stones throw around the coast from Los Cristianos in the south of Tenerife. The general area is in development at the moment but will be a tranquil haven within a couple of years with multi million pound investment and high quality building taking place in the area.\r\n\r\nThe area has wonderful weather and offers a superb climate as it is located between a nature reserve and the Guaza Mountain, ideal for hikers, mountain biking, horse riding or just to enjoy the natural beauty of the Canarian coastline.  Palm is 18 kms from the south airport, a journey that takes around 20 minutes.', 'Palm Mar', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'palm-mar', '', '', '2012-09-22 21:57:47', '2012-09-22 21:57:47', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=447', 0, 'location', '', 0),
