(449, 1, '2012-09-22 21:59:14', '2012-09-22 21:59:14', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/las-galletas.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-450" title="las-galletas" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/las-galletas-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></a>Las Galletas is a fishing village in the municipality of Arona. It has a small harbour and marina but does not have much tourist accommodation, which is available in Costa del Silencio that has grown up on the eastern side of the town.  Las Galletas has a long curved beach that is protected by the harbour quay making the sea extremely calm and ideal for young families.  There are plenty of bars and restaurants in Las Galletas particularly along the promenade.  Las Galletas is 15kms from the south airport, a journey that takes about 20 minutes.', 'Las Galletas', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'las-galletas', '', '', '2012-09-22 21:59:14', '2012-09-22 21:59:14', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=449', 0, 'location', '', 0),
