(452, 1, '2012-09-22 22:20:41', '2012-09-22 22:20:41', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/costa-de-sliencio.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-453" title="costa-de-sliencio" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/costa-de-sliencio-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></a>Costa del Silencio is a small purpose built tourist resort that stands adjacent to La Galletas in the municipality of Arona.  It was the first area of Tenerife to be developed specifically for tourism and was a joint venture between Tenerife and Belgian companies in the early 60’s from which their primary development Tenbel was named.\r\n\r\nThe resort area suffers from not having its own beach although the beach at Las Galletas is but a short walk away.  There is a huge amount of self-catering accommodation in Costa del Silencio, which as a result boasts many shops and supermarkets.  Tenbel is split in four distinct areas with each area boasting its own large swimming pool.  Costa del Silencio is 15kms from the south airport, a journey that takes about 20 minutes.', 'Costa del Silencio', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'costa-del-silencio', '', '', '2012-09-22 22:20:41', '2012-09-22 22:20:41', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=452', 0, 'location', '', 0),
