(454, 1, '2012-09-22 22:25:53', '2012-09-22 22:25:53', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/amarilla-golf.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-455" title="amarilla-golf" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/amarilla-golf-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /></a>Amarilla Golf and Country Club is located in the Municipality of San Miguel de Abona on the southern coast of Tenerife.  Construction commenced in the mid eighties and the Resort area comprises a number of individual residential and holiday complexes constructed within the 18 hole championship golf course, which opened in 1987.   The splendid sea views on offer are complemented by the San Miguel Marina located in the southeast corner of the Golf and Country Club.\r\n\r\nThe resort area, which may be described as rustic in nature is fairly quiet but the leisure and entertainment options of the adjacent and interconnecting Golf del Sur complement those on offer at Amarilla.  The resort is 10kms from the airport, a journey that will take less than 20 minutes.\r\n<em></em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Amarilla Golf and Country Club', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'amarilla-golf-and-country-club', '', '', '2012-09-22 22:26:23', '2012-09-22 22:26:23', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=454', 0, 'location', '', 0),
