(456, 1, '2012-09-22 22:28:33', '2012-09-22 22:28:33', '<a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-del-sur1.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-457" title="golf-del-sur" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/golf-del-sur1-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /></a>Golf del Sur is located in the Municipality of San Miguel de Abona on the southern coast of Tenerife and like its neighbour,\r\n\r\nAmarilla Golf and Country Club, it boasts a number of hotels, residential and holiday complexes built in and around 27 holes of Golf, which make up the Golf course.  Like its neighbour, it lacks a beach, the nearest being located in Las Galletas or El Medano.  Golf del Sur has its own commercial center, San Blas, which has an ample supply of shops, bars and restaurants. There are two large Irish Bars within Golf del Sur and the resort also has a bowling green, situated in the Winter Gardens complex, to which visitors are welcome. The resort is less than 9kms from the airport, a journey that will take 15 minutes.', 'Golf del Sur', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'golf-del-sur-2', '', '', '2012-09-22 22:28:33', '2012-09-22 22:28:33', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=456', 0, 'location', '', 0),
