(524, 1, '2012-09-23 15:28:47', '2012-09-23 15:28:47', '<p><a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/guimar-pyramides.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-526" title="guimar-pyramides" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/guimar-pyramides-300x224.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="224" /></a>If history interests you then visit The Guimar Pyramids Ethnographic Park that is located inland from Tenerife''s east coast in Guimar. These six pyramids are similar to those in Sicily, Mexico, Mesopotamia, Polinesia and Peru and have been extensively researched since the early 1990’s by Norwegian anthropologist, Thor Heyerdahl. The site has an information centre, café, shop and children’s playground. Buses are available from various pick up points in the South of Tenerife.  Trips may be booked thru any excursion agency in Tenerife.</p>', 'Guimar Pyramids', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'guimar-pyramids', '', '', '2012-09-23 15:28:47', '2012-09-23 15:28:47', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=524', 0, 'location', '', 0),
