(561, 1, '2012-09-23 17:54:15', '2012-09-23 17:54:15', '<p><a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/karting-1.png"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-563" title="karting-1" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/karting-1-228x240.png" alt="" width="228" height="240" /></a>With over 25 years of history Karting Club Tenerife offers outstanding facilities. The senior circuit has 1,000 m. length and a track width of at least 8 m. For this circuit there are two types of kart: The Superkart, with 270cc.  for clients over 18 years old and the competition kart for young people aged 15-17 years. Both acquire high speeds in relation to the quality and safety of the circuit. The Junior Circuit is equipped with the highest technical and safety conditions, with its 250 m. length and 8 m. minimum width it is ideal for all children. For this circuit there are three other types of kart: The two-seater, for one adult and one child up to 5 years, the Pony for children from six to nine and Cadet, for children up to 14.</p>\r\n<p>An LED display and a timing system has been installed so all users can enjoy a richer experience. Now you can compare track times either personally or amongst groups, which will increase the enjoyment and competitive experience of karting as a whole. A free shuttle bus available from the resort areas of Los Cristianos and Play de las Americas and the Karting Club Tenerife is continuously open daily from 10:00 to 20:00 and in summer (July and August)</p>', 'Karting Tenerife', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'karting-tenerife', '', '', '2012-09-23 17:54:15', '2012-09-23 17:54:15', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=561', 0, 'location', '', 0),
