(564, 1, '2012-09-23 18:03:13', '2012-09-23 18:03:13', '<p><a href="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/bob-diving-1.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-565" title="bob-diving-1" src="http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/wp-content/uploads/bob-diving-1-300x199.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="199" /></a>All the underwater fun of traditional scuba diving, with much less effort. Despite looking like something secret agent 007 might use, you don''t need to be James Bond to enjoy exploring Tenerife''s underwater world. Our modern underwater scooters can be used by anyone.</p>\r\n<p>They are safe, easy and exciting. Safari BOB in Tenerife is the first BOB diving centre in Europe, operating since 1997, so while on holiday on the island, don’t miss the opportunity to enjoy a fabulous underwater experience that will be the highlight of your trip.</p>\r\n<p>You’ll find Safari BOB Diving in Puerto Colon, Playa de Las Americas, Pier no. 4.</p>', 'Bob Diving', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bob-diving', '', '', '2012-09-23 18:03:13', '2012-09-23 18:03:13', '', 0, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/?post_type=location&#038;p=564', 0, 'location', '', 0),
