(571, 1, '2012-09-20 11:23:15', '2012-09-20 11:23:15', '<h2>Overview</h2>\r\nTenerife is blessed with seven golf courses plus a short nine hole course at Los Palos. The high season for golf in Tenerife runs from October thru to April.  Early booking of tee times is advised during this period with green fees ranging from 80€ up to 200€.\r\n\r\nDuring the off season, May thru to September, it is possible to book a tee time at a moments notice and green fees drop to as little as 40€. In the south of the Island there is also a short nine hole course, Los Palo, where green fees are less than 30€ for 18 holes.\r\n<h2>Golf Courses</h2>\r\n[locations category="13" addresses=”true” type="map" sort_by="title"]', 'Golf Courses', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '297-revision-24', '', '', '2012-09-20 11:23:15', '2012-09-20 11:23:15', '', 297, 'http://tenerife-apartments-online.com/tenerife/297-revision-24/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
